headline.main: Texas Town Looks to Tell Story of Mexican Guest Workers
headline.print_headline: Texas Town Looks to Tell Story of Mexican Guest Workers

lead_paragraph: Northern Irish leaders prepared on Saturday for three weeks of challenging talks to save their devolved government after a snap election that could have dramatic implications for the politics and constitutional status of the British province.
